awc-rules.description:
Entrants who meet the below criteria are eligible to take part:

**1.** Have an established atomic rating on lichess;

**2.** Have played at least 250 rated atomic games on lichess;

**3.** Have had an active playing account on lichess throughout 2018;

**4.** Be participating ONLY using their main account;

**5.** Have messaged the TD (tipau) with an interest in participating;

**6.** Have joined the Atomic World Championship group

Points 1-3 are aimed primarily at preventing duplicate accounts from entering. Entries not meeting these criteria may still be accepted at the TD's/Entry Approval Panel's discretion. 

Exceptions are most likely to be made for players known within the atomic community.

Any player attempting to use multiple accounts or computer assistance will be kicked out and if necessary reported to lichess moderators.
